panels.description: Es werden nur Posts angezeigt, die einen OVP Value von mehr als 2,0 haben.

targets.rawSql:
WITH 
  Calc AS (
    SELECT
    account.name AS Page,
    account.url AS PageURL,
    message,
    description,
    --FIRST_VALUE(message) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as message,
    --FIRST_VALUE(description) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as description,
    postUrl AS PostURL,
    score AS OVP,
    (statistics.actual.sadCount + statistics.actual.angryCount + statistics.actual.hahaCount + statistics.actual.careCount + statistics.actual.wowCount + statistics.actual.loveCount + statistics.actual.thankfulCount + statistics.actual.likeCount) AS ReaktionenActual,
    (statistics.expected.sadCount + statistics.expected.angryCount + statistics.expected.hahaCount + statistics.expected.careCount + statistics.expected.wowCount + statistics.expected.loveCount + statistics.expected.thankfulCount + statistics.expected.likeCount) AS ReaktionenExpected,
    statistics.actual.likeCount AS LikesActual,
    statistics.expected.likeCount AS LikesExpected,
    statistics.actual.commentCount AS CommentsActual,
    statistics.expected.commentCount AS CommentsExpected,
    statistics.actual.shareCount AS SharesActual,
    statistics.expected.shareCount AS SharesExpected,
    TIMESTAMP(date) as Datum,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as rn,
    media[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].url as mediaUrl
    FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.CrowdTangle.${LRA:text}_watchlists`
    WHERE 
    list_name LIKE "${Listen:text}"
  )

SELECT
  Page,
  PageURL,
  CASE
    WHEN message != "not_available" THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(message, r"�", "")
    ELSE
      CASE
        WHEN description != "not_available" THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(description, r"�", "")
        ELSE "<Keine Vorschau des Posts verfügbar>"
      END
  END AS Post,
  PostURL,
  OVP,
  ReaktionenActual,
  ReaktionenExpected,
  ReaktionenActual - ReaktionenExpected AS ReaktionenDiff,
  LikesActual,
  LikesExpected,
  LikesActual - LikesExpected AS LikesDiff,
  CommentsActual,
  CommentsExpected,
  CommentsActual - CommentsExpected AS CommentsDiff,
  SharesActual,
  SharesExpected,
  SharesActual - SharesExpected AS SharesDiff,
  mediaURL,
   Datum
FROM Calc
WHERE OVP >= 2
AND rn = 1
--AND Datum >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR) AND Datum < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()
AND Datum >= ${bq_timeframe_start:doublequote} AND Datum <= ${bq_timeframe_end:doublequote}
ORDER BY OVP DESC
LIMIT 20

targets.rawSql:
WITH 
  Calc AS (
    SELECT
    account.name AS Page,
    account.url AS PageURL,
    message,
    description,
    --FIRST_VALUE(message) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as message,
    --FIRST_VALUE(description) OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as description,
    postUrl AS PostURL,
    ROUND(score,2) AS OVP,
    TIMESTAMP(date) as Datum,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY id ORDER BY score DESC) as rn,
    CASE 
      WHEN media[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].type = "photo"
      THEN media[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].url
      ELSE "keine Vorschau verfügbar"
    END as mediaUrl
    FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.CrowdTangle.${LRA:text}_watchlists`
    WHERE 
    list_name LIKE "${Listen:text}"
  )

SELECT
Page,
  PostURL,
  OVP,  
  mediaURL
  , Datum
FROM Calc
WHERE OVP >= 2
AND rn = 1
--AND Datum >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR) AND Datum < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()
AND Datum >= ${bq_timeframe_start:doublequote} AND Datum <= ${bq_timeframe_end:doublequote}
ORDER BY OVP DESC 
LIMIT 20

targets.rawSql:
WITH Precheck AS (
  SELECT
    ${Listen:value} AS ListenCheck
    FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.CrowdTangle.ct_dataset`
  LIMIT 1
)

SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN ListenCheck IS NULL THEN ERROR("In dieser Liste gab es in den letzten sechs Stunden keine Posts, die overperformed haben.")
  END
FROM Precheck;

SELECT
item.account.name AS Page,
item.account.url AS PageURL,
CASE
  WHEN item.message != "not_available" THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(item.message, r"�", "")
  ELSE
    CASE
      WHEN item.description != "not_available" THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(item.description, r"�", "")
      ELSE "<Keine Vorschau des Posts verfügbar>"
      --WHEN SAFE_CAST(item.title AS STRING) IS NOT NULL THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(item.title, r"�", "")
    END
END AS Post,
item.postUrl as PostURL,
item.score AS OVP,
CONCAT(
  CAST((statistics.actual.sadCount + statistics.actual.angryCount + statistics.actual.hahaCount + statistics.actual.careCount + statistics.actual.wowCount + statistics.actual.loveCount + statistics.actual.thankfulCount + statistics.actual.likeCount) AS STRING), 
  " (", CAST((statistics.expected.sadCount + statistics.expected.angryCount + statistics.expected.hahaCount + statistics.expected.careCount + statistics.expected.wowCount + statistics.expected.loveCount + statistics.expected.thankfulCount + statistics.expected.likeCount) AS STRING), ")"
) as Reaktionen,
CONCAT(
  CAST(statistics.actual.likeCount AS STRING),
  " (", CAST(statistics.expected.likeCount AS STRING), ")"
) as Likes,
CONCAT(
  CAST(statistics.actual.commentCount AS STRING),
  " (", CAST(statistics.expected.commentCount AS STRING), ")"
) as Comments,
CONCAT(
  CAST(statistics.actual.shareCount AS STRING),
  " (", CAST(statistics.expected.shareCount AS STRING), ")"
) as Shares
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.CrowdTangle.ct_dataset`,
UNNEST(`$Listen`) AS item
WHERE item.score >= 2
GROUP BY Page, Post, OVP, Reaktionen, Likes, Comments, Shares, PostURL, PageURL
ORDER BY OVP DESC
LIMIT 20

list.name: Zeitraum

options.value: timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR) AND timestamp < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()
timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 12 HOUR) AND timestamp < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()

date >= (SELECT saturday FROM(SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY) as saturday)) AND date <= (SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY) as sunday)
date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL  7 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()

list.query: Letzte 6 Stunden : timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\, INTERVAL 6 HOUR) AND timestamp < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), Letzte 12 Stunden : timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\, INTERVAL 12 HOUR) AND timestamp < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), Gestern : DATE(timestamp) = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL 1 DAY), Letztes Wochenende :  date >= (SELECT saturday FROM(SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 2 DAY) as saturday)) AND date <= (SELECT DATE(TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()\,WEEK(MONDAY)) - INTERVAL 1 DAY) as sunday), Letzte 7 Tage : date >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  7 DAY) AND date < CURRENT_DATE()

query.rawSql:
SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte 7 Tage" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d", interval_7_day)
     WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Gestern" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)))
    --WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Gestern" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d", yesterday)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letztes Wochenende" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", last_saturday)
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte 6 Stunden" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", DATETIME_SUB(CURRENT_DATETIME(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR))
    WHEN "${Zeitraum:text}" = "Letzte 12 Stunden" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", DATETIME_SUB(CURRENT_DATETIME(), INTERVAL 12 HOUR))
  END AS relevant_value
FROM `grafana.current_date`

SELECT
  CASE "${Zeitraum:text}"
  WHEN "Letztes Wochenende" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d", last_sunday)
  WHEN "Gestern" THEN FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", TIMESTAMP_ADD(TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)), INTERVAL 23 HOUR))
  ELSE FORMAT_TIMESTAMP("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S", TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR))
  END
FROM `grafana.current_date`
